                <summary>David E. Strasburg of the Staunton Spectator office and Miss Emma Kite were
                    married on October 21st at the residence of the bride's mother in Rockingham
                    County. "May the noose of friend Davy's sudden departure be but an augury of his
                    continued happiness--may the future to him and his fair bride be bright with the
                    buds of hope and blossoms of reality--may time deal gently with and eternity
                    await with blissful arms this happy pair."</summary>
                <note/>
